  "business_insights": "================================================================================\nINTERPRETASI OTOMATIS 10 RULES TERATAS\n================================================================================\n\nRule\nJika pelanggan memiliki pola:\nmarket_segment_Direct\nMaka cenderung berkaitan dengan:\ndistribution_channel_Direct, repeated_guest_status_New_Guest, customer_type_Transient\nSupport: 0.114\nConfidence: 0.8442\nLift: 6.9552\n\nRule\nJika pelanggan memiliki pola:\ndistribution_channel_Direct, repeated_guest_status_New_Guest, customer_type_Transient\nMaka cenderung berkaitan dengan:\nmarket_segment_Direct\nSupport: 0.114\nConfidence: 0.9393\nLift: 6.9552\n\nRule\nJika pelanggan memiliki pola:\nmarket_segment_Direct, repeated_guest_status_New_Guest\nMaka cenderung berkaitan dengan:\ndistribution_channel_Direct, customer_type_Transient\nSupport: 0.114\nConfidence: 0.9036\nLift: 6.9081\n\nRule\nJika pelanggan memiliki pola:\ndistribution_channel_Direct, customer_type_Transient\nMaka cenderung berkaitan dengan:\nmarket_segment_Direct, repeated_guest_status_New_Guest\nSupport: 0.114\nConfidence: 0.8716\nLift: 6.9081\n\nRule\nJika pelanggan memiliki pola:\ndistribution_channel_Direct, deposit_type_No Deposit, customer_type_Transient\nMaka cenderung berkaitan dengan:\nmarket_segment_Direct\nSupport: 0.1205\nConfidence: 0.9244\nLift: 6.8454\n\nRule\nJika pelanggan memiliki pola:\nmarket_segment_Direct\nMaka cenderung berkaitan dengan:\ndistribution_channel_Direct, deposit_type_No Deposit, customer_type_Transient\nSupport: 0.1205\nConfidence: 0.8922\nLift: 6.8454\n\nRule\nJika pelanggan memiliki pola:\nmarket_segment_Direct, meal_BB\nMaka cenderung berkaitan dengan:\ndistribution_channel_Direct, customer_type_Transient\nSupport: 0.1039\nConfidence: 0.8936\nLift: 6.8314\n\nRule\nJika pelanggan memiliki pola:\ndistribution_channel_Direct, customer_type_Transient\nMaka cenderung berkaitan dengan:\nmarket_segment_Direct, meal_BB\nSupport: 0.1039\nConfidence: 0.794\nLift: 6.8314\n\nRule\nJika pelanggan memiliki pola:\ndistribution_channel_Direct, customer_type_Transient\nMaka cenderung berkaitan dengan:\nmarket_segment_Direct, deposit_type_No Deposit\nSupport: 0.1205\nConfidence: 0.9211\nLift: 6.8301\n\nRule\nJika pelanggan memiliki pola:\nmarket_segment_Direct, deposit_type_No Deposit\nMaka cenderung berkaitan dengan:\ndistribution_channel_Direct, customer_type_Transient\nSupport: 0.1205\nConfidence: 0.8934\nLift: 6.8301\n================================================================================\nKESIMPULAN OTOMATIS SINGKAT\n================================================================================\n\nBerdasarkan hasil penerapan algoritma Apriori, ditemukan sejumlah frequent itemsets\ndan association rules yang menggambarkan pola perilaku pemesanan pelanggan hotel.\nEvaluasi aturan dilakukan menggunakan support, confidence, dan lift.\n\nRule terbaik berdasarkan kombinasi lift, confidence, dan support:\nAntecedents: market_segment_Direct\nConsequents: distribution_channel_Direct, repeated_guest_status_New_Guest, customer_type_Transient\nSupport: 0.114\nConfidence: 0.8442\nLift: 6.9552\n\nPendekatan tingkat ketepatan seluruh rules: 86.14 %\n\nCatatan laporan:\nIstilah accuracy tidak digunakan secara langsung pada Apriori.\nNilai confidence digunakan sebagai pendekatan tingkat ketepatan aturan asosiasi.\n\n================================================================================\nEXPORT HASIL KE EXCEL\n================================================================================\nFile berhasil disimpan: hasil_lengkap_apriori_hotel_booking.xlsx"
